│ │   - Shareable Canva link             │ │
│ │                                      │ │
│ │ Canva Design Tips                    │ │
│ │                                      │ │
│ │ Typography Hierarchy                 │ │
│ │                                      │ │
│ │ - Headlines: 48-60pt, bold           │ │
│ │ - Subheadings: 32-36pt, medium       │ │
│ │ - Body text: 18-24pt, regular        │ │
│ │ - Captions: 14-16pt, light           │ │
│ │                                      │ │
│ │ Visual Consistency                   │ │
│ │                                      │ │
│ │ - Same phone mockup style throughout │ │
│ │ - Consistent shadow depths           │ │
│ │ - Aligned spacing (use Canva grids)  │ │
│ │ - Repeated color scheme              │ │
│ │                                      │ │
│ │ Animation (if presenting live)       │ │
│ │                                      │ │
│ │ - Subtle fade-ins for features       │ │
│ │ - Slide transitions: smooth dissolve │ │
│ │ - Element animations: minimal,       │ │
│ │ professional                         │ │
│ │                                      │ │
